09:53.193 --> 10:02.068 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AUDIE CORNISH: For the latest on
the ongoing
court battle over President
Trump's executive

10:02.101 --> 10:05.905 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
order on refugees and
