otherwise have covered?

19:36.776 --> 19:41.180 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And there is also
the question
that's been raised about how
much terrorist

19:41.213 --> 19:48.020 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
