20:48.514 --> 20:49.482 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
PHILIP BUMP: Thanks.

20:49.515 --> 20:50.483 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Sure.

20:50.516 --> 21:02.361 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
