has been illegally imprisoning,
torturing

21:32.525 --> 21:35.060 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
and murdering political
opponents.

21:35.094 --> 21:36.262 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
William Brangham has more.

21:36.295 --> 21:39.231 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And a warning: Some of the
details here are
disturbing.

21:39.265 --> 21:45.104 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Amnesty's
report says that
somewhere between 5,000 and
13,000 people

21:45.137 --> 21:52.511 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
were tortured and executed at
one military
prison outside Damascus between
2011 and 2015.

21:52.545 --> 21:56.348 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Amnesty alleges that officials
at the highest
level of the Syrian government
approved the

21:56.382 --> 22:01.153 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
killings, as did the grand mufti
of Syria,
the highest ranking religious
figure in the

22:01.187 --> 22:02.221 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
