22:02.254 --> 22:03.722 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
I'm joined now by Sunjeev Bery.

22:03.756 --> 22:06.859 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
He's Amnesty's director of
advocacy for the
Middle East and North Africa.

22:06.892 --> 22:08.961 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
SUNJEEV BERY, Amnesty
International: Thank
you for having me.

22:08.994 --> 22:12.998 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Very, very
troubling reading
in this report and the stories
of the people

22:13.032 --> 22:15.968 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
