one other senior
level defense official, the
minister of defense.

25:17.216 --> 25:20.285 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: What do you
hope the international
community does with this
evidence?

25:20.319 --> 25:23.989 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SUNJEEV BERY: Well, the first
thing to do
is stare the evidence in the
face and acknowledge

25:24.022 --> 25:25.858 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
what's happening.

25:25.891 --> 25:30.496 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's time for Russia and China
to drop their
veto at the U.N. Security
Council and allow

25:30.529 --> 25:32.965 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
the United Nations to take
action on this.

25:32.998 --> 25:38.504 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
It's time for the U.S.
government under President
Trump to stop pretending that
anything other

25:38.537 --> 25:40.939 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
than gross crimes against
humanity are happening.

25:40.973 --> 25:44.910 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And it's also time to
acknowledge what Syrian
refugees are fleeing.

25:44.943 --> 25:50.549 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
You have perhaps 5,000 to 13,000
people killed
at this prison, another 17,000
people killed

25:50.582 --> 25:55.421 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
