about this.

31:20.045 --> 31:21.747 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Welcome.

31:21.780 --> 31:26.485 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And, Emma, I want to start by
asking you about
what the education secretary can
actually

31:26.518 --> 31:28.320 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
do on her own, right?

31:28.353 --> 31:33.058 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We have seen an administration
that's willing
to use executive power in trying
to deal with

31:33.091 --> 31:34.526 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
regulations.

31:34.559 --> 31:36.561 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
What does that mean for an
education secretary?

31:36.595 --> 31:39.798 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
EMMA BROWN, The Washington Post:
There are
certain things that the
education secretary

31:39.831 --> 31:43.568 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
absolutely can do on her own
now.

31:43.602 --> 31:46.438 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
One of the really important
areas is civil
rights.

31:46.471 --> 31:51.777 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And civil rights advocates are
really worried
actually about what Betsy DeVos
and the Trump

31:51.810 --> 31:54.412 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
administration will do in this
realm.

31:54.446 --> 31:59.651 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
They could really easily with
the stroke of
a pen rescind or revise the
Obama administration's

31:59.684 --> 32:04.923 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
controversial guidance on
transgender students'
accommodations in public
schools.

32:04.956 --> 32:11.997 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Similarly, they can reverse the
guidance that
has really pushed schools and
colleges to

32:12.030 --> 32:13.832 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
handle complaints of sexual
violence differently.

32:13.865 --> 32:19.004 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, there is a whole realm of
civil rights
enforcement and investigation
that is really

32:19.037 --> 32:22.040 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
