33:33.445 --> 33:36.648 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They would have to approve the
legislation
to make it happen.

33:36.681 --> 33:38.450 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
EMMA BROWN: Absolutely.

33:38.483 --> 33:43.288 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And this is where she, Betsy
DeVos, is going
to need cooperation from
Congress, you know,

33:43.321 --> 33:47.926 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
