low-income.

34:03.275 --> 34:05.777 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
So, $20 billion is huge.

34:05.810 --> 34:11.116 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I think that a lot of folks in
the education
community saw that as a really
heavy lift,

34:11.149 --> 34:14.152 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
