against DeVos.

34:14.185 --> 34:17.088 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But there are other ways she can
promote school
choice.

34:17.122 --> 34:20.325 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They can do it through tax code
overhaul.

34:20.358 --> 34:25.096 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
