funded voucher
program here in D.C. -- to
expand that.

34:31.002 --> 34:37.876 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And so there will be, I think,
at least the
beginnings of efforts to expand
school choice,

34:37.909 --> 34:41.746 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
