36:27.786 --> 36:31.156 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN DONVAN: Now, the obstacles
to that ever
happening may seem huge, because
Jason does

36:31.189 --> 36:36.327 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
indeed have autism of a kind
that means he
has quite limited language, so
that only a

36:36.361 --> 36:42.200 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
