37:43.294 --> 37:48.266 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Among Latino children, the gap
is even larger,
at 50 percent.

37:48.299 --> 37:52.904 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Anthony is a clinician and
researcher who
works with a lot of kids who
have autism,

37:52.937 --> 37:54.606 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
