38:54.365 --> 38:56.801 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
DEBRA VINES: There's no special
rec this way.

38:56.834 --> 38:57.869 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Oh.

38:57.902 --> 39:02.073 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
