startup, whose
name is:

39:15.019 --> 39:16.221 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DEBRA VINES: The Answer, Inc.

39:16.254 --> 39:18.022 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN DONVAN: The Answer?

39:18.056 --> 39:22.227 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DEBRA VINES: The Answer, because
so many families
are always asking questions, so
we want to

39:22.260 --> 39:23.962 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
