39:23.995 --> 39:28.633 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JOHN DONVAN: Because she knew,
firsthand,
since Jason was little back in
the 1980s,

39:28.666 --> 39:34.739 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
