community was in being
able to help people like her
boy.

39:34.772 --> 39:39.143 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That's when she had to travel
half-an-hour
by train to get to a support
group, only to

39:39.177 --> 39:40.278 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
