middle- to upper-class
families, so they would drive a
Mercedes.

39:49.087 --> 39:51.756 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
They would, you know, had on
nice jewelry.

39:51.789 --> 39:59.697 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
They had their children with
specialized services,
just an array of things.

39:59.731 --> 40:02.233 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
