40:02.267 --> 40:04.235 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN DONVAN: Did you get a cold
shoulder?

40:04.269 --> 40:06.237 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
DEBRA VINES: Absolutely not.

40:06.271 --> 40:08.273 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
