being underprivileged,

41:46.437 --> 41:54.512 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
underutilized, communities of
color not receiving
proper resources, lack of job
opportunities

41:54.545 --> 41:56.280 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
