I'm on public
assistance, or I can't go to get
this additional

42:07.392 --> 42:10.795 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
help, just because I feel like I
can't do
it.

42:10.828 --> 42:14.132 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN DONVAN: But here's what's
changed around
Maywood.

42:14.165 --> 42:16.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Remember that gala that Debra
was setting
up?

42:16.334 --> 42:22.306 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Well, now it's the night itself,
