42:55.339 --> 42:58.709 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: I feel like I'm not in it
by myself
with The Answer.

42:58.743 --> 43:02.580 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WOMAN: Thank God somebody, you
know, especially
a person of color.

43:02.613 --> 43:08.052 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JOHN DONVAN: There's also a
program called
Just For Men, which James runs.

43:08.085 --> 43:13.124 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Having long since stopped being
embarrassed
by Jason, today, he feels
grateful to have

43:13.157 --> 43:14.926 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
this man as his son.

43:14.959 --> 43:18.296 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JAMES HARLAN: And I tell the men
at the meeting,
I have learned how to love since
I have had

43:18.329 --> 43:19.297 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Jason.

43:19.330 --> 43:20.298 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JOHN DONVAN: More than ever
before?

43:20.331 --> 43:21.299 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JAMES HARLAN: Yes.

43:21.332 --> 43:22.300 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Oh, yes.

43:22.333 --> 43:23.301 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JOHN DONVAN: How so?

43:23.334 --> 43:24.302 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Why?

43:24.335 --> 43:25.303 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JAMES HARLAN: Because he loves
unconditional.

43:25.336 --> 43:28.673 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
