Stephen Richardson, says
autistic kids, autistic

43:47.191 --> 43:48.726 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
adults are all welcome.

43:48.759 --> 43:50.528 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
REV.

43:50.561 --> 43:51.062 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
STEPHEN RICHARDSON, Jordan
Temple Baptist:
