47:06.223 --> 47:11.195 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WOMAN: Timothy McVeigh had
already apparently
been very concerned about what
had happened

47:11.228 --> 47:13.197 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
