tape-recorded interviews

47:50.067 --> 47:56.574 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
about the anger he felt, the
rage he felt
at Ruby Ridge in particular, and
Waco, and

47:56.607 --> 48:01.078 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
the radicalization that happened
in part because
of those events, and, in
